  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Çimen Adventures: Story Teller! Your Imagination Sets the Stage!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a new story waiting to be written! 🎭 In <i>Çimen Maceraları</i>, join Cem and Fazlı as they prank each other and stir up chaos. The goal? Craft the perfect narrative by placing characters and settings to solve puzzles and bring the story to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/0081c05d875378693d3362edfe6e6723.poster.avif?t=1743697048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/0081c05d875378693d3362edfe6e6723.webm?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/0081c05d875378693d3362edfe6e6723.mp4?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag and drop Cem, Fazlı, and their hilarious antics into scenes. Experiment with different combinations to discover unexpected twists and laugh-out-loud outcomes! 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shape the story! Will Cem win hearts, or will Fazlı’s stinginess backfire? Meet familiar faces from the Çimen Talk Show and enjoy seasons packed with clever challenges. ✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/85cd766fdb92157ab61313a51e680cb9.poster.avif?t=1743697048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/85cd766fdb92157ab61313a51e680cb9.webm?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/85cd766fdb92157ab61313a51e680cb9.mp4?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your story, your imagination, your <i>Çimen Maceraları</i>! Download now and start creating! 🚀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/b8536619fd67473fcb8fff5ab342f596.avif?t=1743697048\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras_big/b8536619fd67473fcb8fff5ab342f596.avif?t=1743697048 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Çimen Adventures: Story Teller! Your Imagination Sets the Stage!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a new story waiting to be written! 🎭 In <i>Çimen Maceraları</i>, join Cem and Fazlı as they prank each other and stir up chaos. The goal? Craft the perfect narrative by placing characters and settings to solve puzzles and bring the story to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/0081c05d875378693d3362edfe6e6723.poster.avif?t=1743697048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/0081c05d875378693d3362edfe6e6723.webm?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/0081c05d875378693d3362edfe6e6723.mp4?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag and drop Cem, Fazlı, and their hilarious antics into scenes. Experiment with different combinations to discover unexpected twists and laugh-out-loud outcomes! 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shape the story! Will Cem win hearts, or will Fazlı’s stinginess backfire? Meet familiar faces from the Çimen Talk Show and enjoy seasons packed with clever challenges. ✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/85cd766fdb92157ab61313a51e680cb9.poster.avif?t=1743697048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345580/extras/85cd766fdb92157ab61313a51e680cb9.webm?t=1743697048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets